<section id="gradle_code_analysis" role="wrapper">
	<title>Using code analysis tools
	
		Gradle provides several plugins for analyzing the code base,
		which is being built.
	
	
		<table frame='all'>
			<title>Gradle Code Analysis Tools
			<tgroup cols='3' align='left' colsep='1' rowsep='1'>
